title: Sethupathi movie stills
text:
The stills of Vijay Sethupathi from his forthcoming film 'Sethupathi' with director Arun Kumar (Pannaiyarum Padminiyum) fame has been released for the fans. Vijay Sethupathi will be seen playing a cop role in the movie for the first time. Produced by Vasan Movies, the film has Remya Nambeesan pairing up with Vijay Sethupathi again after 'Pizza'. While the music for the film is by Nivas Prasanna, Sreekar Prasad is handling the editing and Dinesh Krishnan is in charge of the cinematography.
